sd=Product Directory	This service domain maintains a comprehensive directory of the bank's products and services. It can be referenced to obtain product details used to support activities including product selection, sales and marketing, on-boarding, servicing and product fulfillment.	A customer accesses the product directory to obtain product feature descriptions, eligibility and pricing guidelines	The product directory service domain provides a central service to reference product specifications and related details. The broad range of specification information available includes: product feature descriptions; pricing and eligibility requirements used in sales and on-boarding; servicing support and guidelines; and operational and production requirements
sdpath=product-directory
crpath=product-directory-entry
crr=Product Directory Entry Instance
mcr=Product Directory Entry
bqs=Operations SalesandMarketing Servicing Production
CONFIG
ProductDirectoryEntry	register	Register a new product or service in the catalog		registerProductDirectoryEntry		#desc
ProductDirectoryEntry	update	Update details of a product or service in the catalog		updateProductDirectoryEntry		#desc
ProductDirectoryEntry	request	Request that an existing entry is updated or revised		requestProductDirectoryEntry		#desc
ProductDirectoryEntry	retrieve	Retrieve product or service details from the catalog		retrieveProductDirectoryEntry		#desc
